{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168910/extras/Trailer_Proyect_Complete.gif?t=1739760725\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A Cardinal, an expert in the occult, was sent with his acolytes to a remote island. The mission was to unravel the secrets of an ancient civilization... It is your task to find them... But what you will discover will test your faith... and your humanity. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i> </i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u><strong>Description</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lighthouse Of The Souls is a third-person action Roguelite with RPG mechanics and realistic graphics. Face the challenges of a dark world, where survival will depend on your skill and strategy.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168910/extras/Samurai_Scene_1-1.gif?t=1739760725\" /></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u><strong>Demo:</strong></u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Purge Graveyard: The first area is now available.</strong></u></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Explore: Immerse yourself in a realistic, dark and immersive environment.</strong></u></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Face Enemies: Eliminate different enemies, who will test your skills in intense combat.</strong></u></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Upgrade Your Gear: Use the souls you collect to buy and upgrade your equipment.</strong></u></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Develop Your Character: Gain experience and upgrade skills that suit your play style.</strong></u></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Travel Through Portals: Face powerful bosses that represent the ultimate corruption, accessing their domains through portals.</strong></u></p></li><